<p>But the most amazing use of references is in subroutines.  You can
pass code around as if it were data!</p>

<ul>
    <li> Dispatch tables
    <li> Subroutines that work on subroutines -- (e.g., map and grep)
    <li> Dynamically generated subroutines
</ul>

